====Etymology====
From Latin '''[[indignatio]]''', noun of process from perfect passive participle '''[[indignatus]]''', from verb '''[[indignare]]''', from adjective '''[[indignus]]''', ''unworthy'', ''not fitting'', from prefix '''[[in-]]''', ''not'', + '''[[dignus]]''', ''worthy'', ''appropriate''

